1. OVERVIEW

GECB is a free real-time synchronization tool designed to connect Cascadeur and Blender.

The Software consists mainly of two components:

a) Blender-side component
b) Cascadeur-side Python component

The Cascadeur-side Python component is distributed in compiled form because it includes Cascadeur license authentication logic.

