Use of the Software requires a valid paid Cascadeur license, such as Cascadeur Indie, Pro, or Teams.
The Software is not available for use with the free version of Cascadeur.

Open-source components included in this project may be used in accordance with the open-source license provided in the repository.

However, the compiled Cascadeur-side component and its license authentication logic are not open source and are subject to the restrictions described in this EULA.

